{"tid":1845083,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"哩啲係咪叫喜歡","createTime":"2020-01-27T03:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T03:57:56.000Z","uid":14440,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e87aedbea875e243cf08a2c7659a7a6e8baf1e0","tid":1845083,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"次次你哄埋嚟 我個心都跳得好快<br />\n當有啲小小嘅身體接觸 我就會竊喜<br />\n見到你笑我又會跟住笑<br />\n彈緊琴嘅你簡直係識發光<br />\n愈嚟愈期待下次見到你 話題都諗好埋<br />\n雖然諗完最後都係唔會講<br />\n<br />\n不過 真係好想見到你<br />\n好想喺你笑嘅時候搣下你塊面<br />\n好想喺你頭髮亂咗嘅時候替你整理<br />\n好想喺你表演完一曲之後錫啖你<br />\n<br />\n不過 我都係要藏起哩啲心思<br />\n停留喺幻想層面就夠<br />\n唔可以再多<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f892e5e6f7f76bac4b16106a40540b80383dd3f","tid":1845083,"uid":321800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5c36582cb0398bdfddef4698d0f892889c3058","tid":1845083,"uid":14440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:36:45.000Z","msg":"有咩方法可以無咁鍾意你"},{"pid":"081959deed2adf129549aa0e06cf06b1fedd8282","tid":1845083,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"叫變態"},{"pid":"9f1b7e80ebbb7739967c500231394e96d0a69635","tid":1845083,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"081959deed2adf129549aa0e06cf06b1fedd8282","tid":1845083,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"叫變態"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住 咁我都係摺返埋先"},{"pid":"fdc086d71f8f257dd089c95201bd6e2b83052af3","tid":1845083,"uid":131078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"發光就一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25bf72a1827c0021a168052a47459defee095be","tid":1845083,"uid":7